Take a @bread bun{} and slice it in half. Spread @pizza sauce{} on each half.

Sprinkle shredded @cheese{} on top of the sauce on both halves.

Add @pepperoni{} and sprinkle shredded @onion{10%g} on the pizza.

Bake the pizza in the oven at 375F (190C) for ~{8%minutes}, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.

Serve hot and enjoy your delicious bread-crust pizza!
